    • setMeetingDaysAndTime

      public void setMeetingDaysAndTime(String meetingDays, int startTime, int endTime)
      sets the Course's meeting day and time
      Parameters:
      meetingDays - the meeting day string
      startTime - the starting time for course
      endTime - the end time for the course
      Throws:
      IllegalArgumentException - meetingDays invalid
      IllegalArgumentException - meeting days consist of any characters other than ‘M’, ‘T’, ‘W’, ‘H’, ‘F’, or ‘A’
      IllegalArgumentException - meeting days have a duplicate character
      IllegalArgumentException - if ‘A’ is in the meeting days list, it must be the only character
      IllegalArgumentException - he start time is not between 0000 and 2359 an invalid military time
      IllegalArgumentException - the end time is not between 0000 and 2359 or an invalid military time
      IllegalArgumentException - the end time is less than the start time (i.e., no overnight classes)
      IllegalArgumentException - a start time and/or end time is listed when meeting days is ‘A’
